BUFS is a list of buffer, FNS a list of function names."
  (let* ((collection (append (delve--all-delve-buffers-for-completion bufs)
			     (mapcar (lambda (fn)
				       (cons (delve-prettify-delve-fn-doc (delve-get-fn-documentation fn))
